channel.title: StabbingScape[DELTA] spirit shields, corp beast real gs stance & emote. UPDATED!
channel.description:
Hey there. i had this coded already for like 4 months so ive decided to finally release it. heres what ive done.. *i made d claw spec for 8002 it was hard lol. then i found out there was already a dclaw that wasnt 8002. so i got the custom for nothin. now theres 2 d claws lol. *Added a few customs and gave them bonuses. *made the files hidden in the client folder. just unhidden em and it's a decent client base. *attempted to add eventmanager. but that didnt go out so well. * Made it a little like czar.. ::afk ::back ::jump ::jumpoff ::home ::skills ::shops. and added 1 tele tab lol. * made a players online thing. thanks to atrix676 of sinzscape lol * Corp beast, i made it drop sigils. buy a spirit shield from shop and use em together to make a better spirit shield. *made more tele tabs for em czar lovers out there *funpk is much faster now. *added more customs, vesta, statius, mod+admin+owner capes.
some custom item list.. forgot to add in shops :17144 admin cape :17143 mod cape :17145 owner cape :19003 bandos boots.
* real gs stance thanks to SilentCJ. * new jail *new client. added ip changer. aswell with more customs * Stable to support a lot of people. (a lot better then my czar) :P * new random event * i worked on this but i think it already had.. SYIblocker and antinull. sying works but they wont do any damage. they will just get banned for flooding after 5secs of sying. V2 will include..... *Corp beast that drops sigils. *Spirit shields, Morrgians, Vesta, Statius, Winged capes, mod admin owner capes. *more tele tabs, talking npcs, "playername" has logged in * New client with ip changer. Client includes all files, good client base to use if you're interested. I did a lot more just cant remember most of it ;P heres sum pics. Same home just like in my czar sources [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/312izb8.png[/img] Real gs stants, new right click, and that theiving stall gives 5m each time! [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/a2tduc.png[/img] Shops [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2yzn5hu.png[/img] Skills [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2ltqa87.png[/img] Staffzone made by pkjad [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/2lmkmc1.png[/img] Starting Gear [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/zu2ur8.png[/img] Team PK [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/elb68x.png[/img] Bounty Hunter [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/saut83.png[/img] Corp beast [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/ngqci.png[/img] More customs! :D [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/23mk7zl.png[/img] New client (Great base!) [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/6tmk3p.png[/img] tele tabs [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/eiwp5w.png[/img] Commands [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2lwlovr.png[/img] D claw spec, Statius has spec too, and vista longsword just didnt put in pic lol [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/261j1bn.png[/img] hope u like source + client ;) [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/2iglth4.png[/img] i asure you that there are no viruses, forgot to make pic. This is my first time coding a delta source so dont flame. lol. Credits Pkjad delta I weed i atrix676 CilentCJ and many more people i got stuff from that i dont remember of. Links ----------source------------- http://uppit.com/v/KA42A14X ----------------------------- ----------client-------------- http://uppit.com/v/Y8XIRJ39 ----------------------------- Have fun with source for thos of you that download and use it. ;) if anyone needs help add meh at stabbinscape@hotmail.com i love u, i weed i
